<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Service OTP</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff5722;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777777;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #ff5722;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="header">Your Service is Completed!</h2>
        <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for availing our service at <strong>zenLook</strong>. Your service has been successfully completed.</p>

        <p>Here is the verification OTP:</p>
        <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>

        <p>Please share this OTP with the salon owner for verification purposes.</p>

        

        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{currentYear}} zenLook. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
